While citations are not technically necessary on this project, there are a few cases where they will be advocated (and the <nowiki>{{citation needed}}</nowiki> template used):

* Pages documenting [[events|tags/Events]], especially [[current ones|tags/Current_events]]
* Pages documenting [[people|tags/People]], especially living ones
* Quotations, transcriptions, and statements
* Figures (i.e. trading volume of an exchange)
* Controversial or far-fetched information
